    "Future research should focus on enhancing the model's analytical capabilities, refining its ability to engage with complex methodological critiques, and expanding its capacity for identifying subtle theoretical implications.Addressing the ethical considerations and potential biases inherent in AI-assisted research emerges as a crucial area for ongoing inquiry, emphasizing the need for transparent methodologies and diverse, representative training datasets.",
